# Heat Equation Simulation Project

The main showcase of this project is cuda and openGL interop. Where we can leverage high performance from cuda and get real time rendering via cuda. 



# Sources Used

* [https://github.com/NVIDIA/cuda-samples](Cuda Samples by NVIDIA)
    * [https://github.com/NVIDIA/cuda-samples/tree/master/Samples/5_Domain_Specific/fluidsGL](Fluid Rendering with OpenGL)
    * [https://github.com/NVIDIA/cuda-samples/tree/master/Samples/5_Domain_Specific/simpleGL](Example 3D Cos-Sin Graph with OpenGL)
* [https://enccs.github.io/OpenACC-CUDA-beginners/2.02_cuda-heat-equation/](Cuda Heat Equation)
